Question: Which Language*?
Constraint/Rule: if (Language*.Java) {Language = true;}if (Language*.Python) {Language = true;}if (Language*.PHP) {Language = true;}if (Language*.Perl) {Language = true;}if (Language*.Java) {LicenseCostFee* = US;}if (Language*.Perl) {Storage* = FileRCS;}if (Language*.Python) {disAllow(Storage*.Database);}

Question: Which License?
Constraint/Rule: if (License.GPL) {Storage = true;}if (License.GPL2) {Language* = PHP;}if (License.NoLimit) {disAllow(LicenseCostFee*.DifferentLicenses);}if(License.GPL) {disAllow(LicenseCostFee.DifferentLicenses);}if (License.Commercial) {LicenseCostFee* = US;}if (LicenseCostFee*.US) {License = Commercial;}if (License.NoLimit) {Unicode = false;}

Question: Which Storage*?
Constraint/Rule: if (Storage*.Files) {Storage = true;}if (Storage*.Database) {Storage = true;}if (Storage*.FileRCS) {Storage = true;}if (Storage*.Database) {disAllow(Language*.Python);}if (Storage*.FileRCS) {Language* = Perl;}if (Storage*.FileRCS) {LicenseCostFee* = Community;}if (Storage*.Files) {LicenseCostFee = false;}
